These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, nectarine
1. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
2. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | milk  | almond-milk |
| Food       | lettuce | nectarine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, cycling
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | milk | lemonade |
| Sport      | cycling     | climbing  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, mystery
There are 2 different nationalities: mexican, malaysian
1. the mexican is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the mexican is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | mystery  |
| Nationality   | mexican | malaysian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
